              <section id="article-content-123443" class="item article-body default-color mb-6 mt-5">
                  <p>文：阿康</p> <p>這系列文章我將陸續整理了一些常見謬誤的學習方法，不少理論或概念其實常常會出現在各類文章和書籍上頭，我平常有在收集這方向的研究和資料，覺得大家應該也會有興趣，你也不妨看看自己是否仍相信這些論點，又或者還在使用這些學習方法。</p><div class="ad-content " style="min-height:326px">
    <div class="tmgad tmgad-name-tnl_a_p2 tmgad-type-general tmgad-new" style="">
  <script type="application/json">{"type":"general","targeting":{"cabinet":["555675","9e2a87a6-6aa8-4b89-a2ad-7172f47829e4"],"advertising":["0"],"sponsor":["0"],"paid":["0"],"page_key":["article"],"page_name":["article"],"tag_key":["57668","131224","143234","177785","193811","200935","200936","200937","200938","200939"],"tag_name":["\u6559\u80b2\u5fc3\u7406\u5b78","\u5927\u8166\u79d1\u5b78","\u5b78\u7fd2\u65b9\u6cd5","\u6253\u7834\u5927\u8166\u507d\u79d1\u5b78","\u5b78\u7fd2\u91d1\u5b57\u5854","\u5b78\u7fd2\u98a8\u683c","\u4e3b\u52d5\u5b78\u7fd2","\u88ab\u52d5\u5b78\u7fd2","\u5de6\u53f3\u8166\u6e2c\u8a66","\u4f60\u6709\u4f60\u7684\u8a08\u5283\uff0c\u4e16\u754c\u53e6\u6709\u8a08\u5283"],"author_key":["newsveg"],"author_name":["\u751f\u9bae\u6642\u66f8"],"category_key":["education"],"category_name":["\u6559\u80b2"],"type_key":["review"],"type_name":["\u8a55\u8ad6"]},"slot":"\/21870649235\/tnl_a_p2","size":[[640,480],[640,360],[300,250],[1,1]],"mapping":[[[970,0],[[640,480],[640,360],[1,1]]],[[336,0],[[300,250],[1,1]]]],"name":"tnl_a_p2"}</script>
